string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1_Ino_2_idle_s
string.body: Hey! Please listen to what I've got to say.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1_Ino_3_idle_s
string.body: We have a big problem! Krall are plotting, plotting something.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_015_Die_S
string.body: Grrrk, you know how to play.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_016_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, you are not leaving just like that.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_030_Die_S
string.body: Please avenge my death, my lord Saendukal...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_035_Batk_S
string.body: Today... shall be the day... you die...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_038_Katk_S
string.body: Leave... if you don't want to die...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_040_Die_S
string.body: I'd rather have an eternal rest...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_041_Batk_B
string.body: You will regret... having come here, [%userclass]...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_052_Katk_S
string.body: Kraark, I'll show you the power of magic!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_053_Die_S
string.body: Grrrk, I will never forgive you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_060_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, it's been a while since I last tasted blood!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_065_Die_S
string.body: Grrrk, you are not bad at all...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_066_Die_S
string.body: Please avenge my death, my lord Saendukal...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_071_Katk_S
string.body: Kraark, I'll give you a hot lesson!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_076_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, how dare you come here!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_078_Katk_S
string.body: You not so bad. Worthy opponent!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_084_Katk_S
string.body: Here, just take two more hits!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_085_Katk_S
string.body: Here, just take one more hit!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_095_Batk_S
string.body: You don't seem to be afraid of me.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_097_Die_S
string.body: It hurts, I don't want to die.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_098_Idle_S
string.body: I worked too long and I'm tired.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_099_Idle_S
string.body: I can't work, I'm too hungry.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_100_Batk_S
string.body: I'll hit you just a little.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_102_Atk_S
string.body: Just go down already, blast it...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_103_Flee_S
string.body: Spare me! I only did what I was told to do.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_104_Die_S
string.body: There are still so many things to do...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_105_Die_S
string.body: So, this is how Kobold dies...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_106_Idle_S
string.body: I work too much. It's hard.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_107_Idle_S
string.body: And they don't even give us enough food to live on! What a life, nyerk.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_113_Die_S
string.body: I want to be born as a Krall in next life...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_002
string.body: The meal-time bell has rung! Time to eat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_003
string.body: It's the meal-time bell! Time to eat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_005
string.body: I'm very hungry! I'm going to eat and eat a lot.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_119_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, what an absurd pup! Daring to attack me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_120_Katk_S
string.body: I shall soak this place with your blood!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_123_Katk_S
string.body: I'll show you the true horror!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_124_Die_S
string.body: How, how did I... To, to a mere Elyos...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_125_Die_S
string.body: I will never forget this shame...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_127_Idle_S
string.body: I will brief you on your mission.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_128_Idle_S
string.body: The time has come to reveal the hidden power of the Elyos.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_129_Atk_S
string.body: [%userclass], someone is waiting for you at the Outer Dock!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_130_Atk_S
string.body: Hey, [%userclass], go to the Outer Dock!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_131_Atk_S
string.body: Go and talk to Bella in the Outer Dock.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_132_Atk_S
string.body: Hey you [%userclass], what are you dallying about?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_133_Atk_S
string.body: Leave this place to me and just go!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_134_Atk_S
string.body: Are you [%username]? Let us leave quickly!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_137_Atk_S
string.body: Are you all right over there?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_138_Eatk_S
string.body: So, there is one less after this...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_139_Batk_S
string.body: There is not even a moment to rest, eh...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_141_Atk_S
string.body: I won't let you get away from me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_142_Eatk_S
string.body: You will not set a single foot in here as long as I'm around!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_144_Atk_S
string.body: Get out of here right now!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_150_Eatk_S
string.body: Just when is the reinforcement going to come...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_153_Idle_S
string.body: The shaman is looking for you [%usergender], so go quickly.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_154_Idle_S
string.body: The shaman is waiting for you below the ruins to the northwest from here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_155_Idle_S
string.body: I sense something ominous in the west.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_156_Idle_S
string.body: What will be the fate of Elysea...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_160_Idle_S
string.body: Now even they are... Just what are they intending to do?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_161_Idle_S
string.body: Lately, I've been seeing a number of shady characters.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_162_Idle_S
string.body: I hear there are some curious creatures in the Krall encampment.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_164_Idle_S
string.body: Are you here to receive supplies?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_166_Idle_S
string.body: Hold this place with your life!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_167_Batk_S
string.body: Confound it, they are here again!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_170_Eatk_S
string.body: I'm so sick and tired of these battles!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_171_Batk_S
string.body: Hahaha! You dare to attack me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_FIELDOBJECT_001
string.body: It cannot be used right now.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_SHANDURA_001
string.body: You'll see how fearsome this sword is!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_181_Idle_S
string.body: Are you [%username]? I have been waiting for you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_182_Idle_S
string.body: Are you the [%userclass] who volunteered for the advance party?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_183
string.body: You cowards, ganging up like this on just one foe!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_184_Atk_S
string.body: It's all right! We can win!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_185_Atk_S
string.body: Keep it up for just a little longer.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_186_Atk_S
string.body: You will not escape from here!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_188_Atk_S
string.body: You aren't so bad for a Krall!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_189_Atk_S
string.body: You are no match for me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_191_Atk_S
string.body: Ugh, you are not bad at all...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_192_Idle_S
string.body: Oh no, the shaman's prophecy is really going to...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_199_Atk_S
string.body: You aren't so bad, are you? But still there is no way you will defeat me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_200_Idle_S
string.body: There must be something important to take care of, [%usergender], for you to have come all the way here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_201_Idle_S
string.body: There are many Krall about, so be careful around here!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_202_Idle_S
string.body: When the bell rings we eat.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_203_Idle_S
string.body: I want to eat. Ring the bell.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_205_Idle_S
string.body: I'm hungry. I hope the bell rings soon.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_HELP_002
string.body: Master gave an order! Kobold attack!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_WARNING_BELL_002
string.body: It is the alarm! Kraark, what is happening?

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_WARNING_BELL_003
string.body: Kraark, good. It's been a while since I had a workout!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_206_Katk_S
string.body: Rise again, the spirit of Darkness!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_207_Katk_S
string.body: Answer my call, the spirit of the dead!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_208_Katk_S
string.body: O walking deads, fight for Lord Saendukal!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_MUSHROOM_POLYMORPH_001
string.body: You feel a strange sensation. You have turned into a mushroom.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_GOBLIN_MANAGER_001
string.body: I do not run! I fight to the end!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1A_LUSIS_1_Waypoint
string.body: The Kobolds are rather quiet today.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1A_Naia_1_WayPoint
string.body: The porgus is quite fat, looks like Cannon has been feeding it well.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_NPC_Ulaguru_2_idle_s
string.body: Kraark, I'm hungry. Marmeia! When are you going to feed me?

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_NPC_Ulaguru_3_idle_s
string.body: Kraark, Krall are much stronger than Daevas!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LC1_NPC_Ulaguru_4_idle_s
string.body: Kraark, you better be prepared! Soon my brothers will come to rescue me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_003_Idle_S
string.body: Wow! It is the Protector of Sanctum, [%username]!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_004_Idle_S
string.body: Now that [%username] is here, the tide of the battle should turn in our favor.

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_013_Atk_S
string.body: We will not let you wretches to take the Abyss!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_015_Atk_S
string.body: So, what do you think? The power of Pandaemonium, that is!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_018_Atk_S
string.body: Do you sense the power of Archon?

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_022_Idle_S
string.body: [%username], please show those wretches the might of Sanctum!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_024_Batk_S
string.body: I smell an Elyos. There is an intruder!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_025_Batk_S
string.body: It is the punishment of Lord Orissan!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_030_Batk_S
string.body: Who the hell is it? Who dares to disturb my slumber!

string.name: STR_CHAT_AbPRo_033_Die_S
string.body: What a shameful way to die, defeated by a Guardian!

string.name: STR_CHAT_postman_03_Idle_B
string.body: Time is silver my friend, akakak!

string.name: STR_CHAT_postman_04_Idle_B
string.body: There is no mail for you, nyerk.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Farmer_002_Atk_B
string.body: I spent so much time and effort to grow these crops!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_001_Atk_S
string.body: There is just no end to them and they keep coming!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_002_Atk_S
string.body: These accursed wretches do not even tire!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Shugo_001_Idle_S
string.body: We have some nice stuff! Come and have a look, akakak.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Shugo_002_Idle_S
string.body: Do you want to have a look at the Shugo specialties?

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_001_Idle_S
string.body: The Kerubs have been particularly persistent lately.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_002_Idle_S
string.body: We really are in big trouble, with all our crops plundered.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_003_Idle_S
string.body: I believe even the Akarios village is in danger right now.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_004_Idle_S
string.body: The Daminu forest is also quite eerie.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_004_Idle_S
string.body: Hey, keep quiet over there! All the fish are getting away!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_005_Idle_S
string.body: The movements of the Kobolds have been quite suspicious.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1Guard_006_Idle_S
string.body: Those darned Krall, just what do they have in mind, I wonder?

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_005_Idle_S
string.body: Ouch, my back! My whole body is aching.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1NPC_007_Idle_S
string.body: There is something ominous about the flow of Aether.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aGuard_001_Idle_S
string.body: The movements of Tursin of late have been...

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aGuard_002_Idle_S
string.body: Yet another large scale battle has begun in the Abyss.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_001_Idle_B
string.body: Nesia has given birth to a son!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1aBroadCaster_002_Idle_B
string.body: Please be careful! There are lots of things floating in the sky above the Citadel nowadays.
